  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Rohan, the monsoon drizzle makes me think of perfect passes and sudden goals — how’s your training these days?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "We had a friendly match last weekend! I scored a goal, but my passing could be better. I watch some Bengali football movies to get inspired. How about you, play any football?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds exciting. Scoring a goal is always a high. What’s your favorite Bengali football movie?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite is Goal! The Movie. It’s not real life, but it makes me feel happy. I also like to take photos of football matches sometimes. The light during monsoon is so nice for pictures. Do you like photography?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The monsoon light is magical for photos, it softens everything. I admire that you find joy in both football and photography. Do you have a favorite shot from a match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "There’s one shot of a player scoring during rain — the ball, the net, the crowd — all blurred but clear at same time. I took it last monsoon. I think it’s my best photo yet! But I still need to work on my passing. Maybe I can practice more."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a special photo — how did it feel when you took it? And your idea to practice more shows you’re growing, just like your passing will get better with time. What’s your next step?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Next step is to practice with my local team more. I also want to try taking photos of fast action — maybe that helps me with timing in football too. Easier said than done, right? 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I love that idea — photography and football can sharpen each other’s timing. What’s one thing you’ll try this week to get started?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "This week, I’ll try to take 10 photos during a match — of passes, shots, maybe even my own team. And I’ll practice passing for 30 minutes every day. I think consistency is key, na? Let’s see how it goes!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're planning it perfectly — 10 shots and daily practice show great focus. Consistency really does make the difference. How will you track your progress?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I’ll use my phone to save the photos and a notebook for passing practice — like, write down what I did each day. Maybe even ask my coach to check my notes? It’s a start, na? I’ll keep you updated, promise! 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds smart — a phone, a notebook, and a coach are a great mix. I'll wait to hear how it goes! What’s one challenge you expect with this plan?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "One challenge might be finding time — I have bank exam prep too, so balancing all could be tough. Sometimes I get so into football that I forget my study time! But I’ll try my best. Thank you for asking, Maya! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re very welcome — balancing bank prep and football is no small task! What’s one small win you’ll celebrate this week to stay motivated?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "A small win could be taking all 10 photos during the match and practicing passing without getting distracted by my phone. Even if it’s just 10 minutes extra, I’ll treat myself to my favorite chai! It keeps me going, you know? 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Chai is the perfect fuel — 10 minutes extra and a photo goal sound just right. What match are you planning to shoot next?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The local league match on Saturday — my team is playing against the old rivals! It’s always intense, but the best for practice. I’ll try to capture some good moments and maybe even get a shot of the coach shouting orders! You know, it’s like a little drama, na? 😄 I should get going now — got to revise some banking terms. Talk to you later, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a plan — capturing the coach and the drama is a great idea! Revising banking terms — you’ve got this! Talk soon, Rohan."
    }
  ],
